title: DIGITUS Cable Guide Bracket 44 x 100 mm - 10 Pieces - Network Cabinet 19 Inches - Cable Management - Grey
description:
About this item
Cable management rings play the role of cable ducts in the server cabinet. Network cables can be easily added or removed from the harness when you change settings.
It makes sense to place some guide brackets up, down, and in the center as fixed points in the cabinet. Two central management rings above and below cable ducts or patch panels are also conceivable.
The rings, which are made of robust sheet steel, can be screwed to a height unit. In network cabinets, profiled rails are usually located at the front and at the rear of the cabinet.
In addition to patch and fiber optic cables, power lines can also be optimized with cable routing. Like cable routing panels, guide brackets can also be used in control cabinets.
A sales unit always contains 10 manoeuvring brackets and the necessary fixing material such as cage nuts and bolts.

title: Trimax Universal Stainless Steel Receiver Lock - Fits 1/2" & 5/8" With Sleeve SXTS32, Clam Packaging
description:
TRIMAX Corporation is the world's leading lock manufacturer providing customers' high quality products through innovative design
Clam Packaging

› See more product details
desc2: Trimax SXTS32 Dare to compare! TRIMAX, the leader in Receiver Locking Pins, has spent the last 10 years expanding and improving on the "ORIGINAL." The Patented Dual Lock Lug Design offers over 5,800 lbs. of head pull strength. A 1/4 turn of the rugged tube key locks & unlocks the strongest locking pin on the market. Don't settle for low quality knockoffs! The SXTS32 converts from a 1/2" to a 5/8" pin with a stainless steel sleeve and features premium 100% stainless steel. Provides instant security for your camper, boat or trailer by securing your vehicle trailer hitch. No internal springs to seize or brake. Knurling on lock heads adds style and grip and is machined from 100% solid forged steel. Double headed or "dog bone" style design. Width between heads (exposed pin length or gap space) is 2-5/8". A receiver pin is used to secure the receptacle part of a trailer hitch (attached to a vehicle) to inserts such as ball mounts, drawbars, accessory carriers or ornamental receiver plugs. The most common receiver pins are 1/2" and 5/8" in diameter. Class II receiver hitches have 1-1/4" receptacles and use 1/2" pins. Class III, IV and V receiver hitches have 2" receptacles and use 5/8" pins. TRIMAX makes the world's toughest locks. Through value added engineering design, TRIMAX is committed to product innovation that holds up to the highest quality standards. TRIMAX provides maximum security for marine, trailer and tow, RV, performance truck, power sports and bicycle applications. Tested. Tough. TRIMAX. TRIMAX offers a lifetime warranty on all of their products.

title: Hepco & Becker Sidecarrier Lock-it - black for Kawasaki Versys 650 from 2015 | 6502522 00 01
desc2:
Excellent fit – every Hepco & Becker lock-it side carrier is precisely matched to the respective motorcycle type. This results in a very high fit of the carrier on the motorcycle. Made from tubular steel and custom-made laser parts, which are reinforced once again in heavily stressed areas. The quality of the lock-it straps has been confirmed several times in specialist magazines.

The straps can be mounted and removed in seconds. You only need to loosen the attached lock-it screws with a quarter turn and you can take the side parts back or to the side. Ensure good air and a feel-good climate in all rooms - with our Beurer air washer LW 230.

desc2: Auriga Features the family of Ultra Wide Angle 82° apparent field eyepieces, 31.8mm barrel and FMC anti-glare treatment. The Auriga UWA series consists of 4mm, 7mm, 10mm, 13mm and 16mm eyepieces, respectively. The UWA Auriga series eyepieces are composed of 7 elements divided into 4 groups. The sophisticated optical scheme of which these eyepieces are composed guarantees an exceptional experience of use on any type of instrument, even the least bright. The sharpness and contrast of these eyepieces, along with the 82° apparent field will make your observations engaging and unforgettable. It will be like opening a window directly to the beauties of the Cosmos. Pupillary extraction of all Auriga UWA eyepieces is 12mm. The performance at the edges of the field is excellent and no reflections or artifacts are observed. The FMC anti-reflective treatment ensures very high levels of modulation in contrast to sharp, bright, well-defined images without artifacts. The 31.8 mm barrel is made of aluminium with CNC machines and is equipped with a comfortable rubber handle, for a firm and effective grip even when wearing gloves.

desc2: Auriga Features the family of 65° wide angle eyepieces of apparent field, 31.8mm barrel and FMC anti-reflective treatment. The Auriga WA series consists of three eyepieces respectively of 12mm, 17mm and 20mm. The eyepieces of the WA Auriga series consist of 4 elements. The optical scheme of which these eyepieces are composed guarantees an exceptional experience of use in each type of instrument. The apparent 65° field is the ideal compromise for those looking for high price-performance eyes and as an upgrade to those found in standards in entry-level and mid-level astronomical instruments. The sharpness and contrast of these eyepieces will surprise even the most careful and scrupulous observers. Amazing observations of the lunar, solar surface, planets and even deep sky objects await you. All eyepieces are characterized by a pupillary extraction of 17 mm. The performance at the edges of the field is good and no reflections or spurred artifacts are observed. FMC anti-reflective treatment ensures high levels of modulation in contrast to sharp, bright, well-defined and artifact-free images.

desc2:
Nitecore BP23 Rugtas – De BP23 is het nieuwe lid van de Nitecore Rugtas serie. Hij heeft een grosse capaciteit en een gebruiksvriendelijker ontwerp, en voldoet voor de meeste gebruikers aan de daadwerkelijke ferro van het dagelijkse woon-werkverkeer. De BP23 rugtas heeft een inhoud van 23 litri con quattro compartimenti waarbij het hoofdvak 7 vakken heeft voor het organizza van bobine di condensazione. Het laptopvak is groot genoeg voor een 15,6" laptop che sono stati recuperati da schokbestendig en stootvast. Bovendien heeft het voorvak een completamente aperto con 4 secties, wat handig is voor de toegang tot grote voorwerpen. De speciale drievoudige verdeler zorgt voor snelle toegang morto per ogni bobine di direzioni iridescenti.

In het buitenste compartiment van de BP23 zorgt de gebruiksvriendelijke schuine rits voor het soepeler openen en sluiten, zodat je er gemakkelijker bij kunt als je hem tijdens het woon-werkverkeer met én riem over je schouder draagt. Het bovenste compartiment met kussentjesvoering is ontworpen voor het opbergen van bobine come smartphone e occhiali da sole gemakkelijk krassen op lopen.

De rugtas heeft handvatten aan quattro zijden zodat je hem op assottiglianti maniere kunt dragen. Met de Quick Release Schouderbanden kun je hem makkelijk en comfortable op je rug dragen. Daarnaast heeft de rugtas een zeer goede ventilatie op de ottagonale en is het voorzien van het Molle systeem en lussen voor bevestiging van extra uitrusting, piccole tazze di bagni. Deze rugtas is gemaakt van duurzaam 600D nylon en het gecoate oppervlak is vuil- en waterafstotend. De binnenvoering is uitgevoerd in goed zichtbaar oranje zodat je ook bij wine light je bobine kunt vinden.

title: Salt & Pepper Games | Unreliable Wizard | Card Board Game | Solitaire Game to Become A Wizard and Unleash Heroes | 1 Player | Spanish and English
description:
About this item
Experience an engaging solo gameplay as an apprentice wizard on a mission to save the princess by defeating the Demon Lord in this strategic card game.
With just 32 cards, the game offers a rich and strategic experience where you move across a map, manage life points, and overcome various challenges.
Utilize a hand of cards to create powerful magic by matching specific patterns. Enhance your abilities by collecting new spells and recruiting traveling companions.
Navigate through different terrains that require life points to cross and engage in battles against enemy minions at designated points on the map.
Gain new cards, including additional spells and companions, as rewards for defeating enemies. Successfully defeat the Demon Lord at the end of the map to win the game and save the princess.
› See more product details
desc2: You are an apprentice wizard tasked by the King with destroying the Demon Lord and thus saving the Princess. This card based solo game has you advancing along the map fighting enemy minions and gathering new magic and traveling companions to assist along the way. The game consists of 32 cards. you move your wizard along the map and pay Life Points to cross terrain. Certain terrain are battle points where you battle enemy minions. You use your hand of cards to create magic by matching certain magic patterns, your traveling companions may apply skills as well. If you defeat the evil minions you gain more cards which may contain magic or traveling companions. If you defeat the Demon King at the end of the map you win!

title: Salt & Pepper Games | The Battle of Versailles | Compete to Be The Most Influential Designer in This Card Game for 2 Players | Game in English for Ages 14 and Up
description:
About this item
Players engage in a fashion face-off, representing either the U.S. Gold French team, mimicking the 1973 fashion showdown at Versailles. Each team employs unique strategies to gain prestige in the fashion world.
Reflecting the real event, the French team has five actions per round, representing their long, traditional show, while the American team has three actions per round, mirroring their short, innovative presentation.This difference creates distinct tactical approaches for each team.
The French team focuses on maintaining their prestige and contributing to the reconstruction of Versailles, while the American team aims to steal French prestige and showcase their innovative fashion features.
Players compete to control the most influential celebrities in the fashion world and can use action cards to spread gossip, adding an extra layer of strategy and interaction.
The game immerses players in the historical and cultural significance of the 1973 event, blending fashion history with strategic gameplay, making it both educational and entertaining.
› See more product details
desc2: The Battle of Versailles" was a fashion show held in 1973 in Versailles, France that pitted five American designers against five French designers. The American designers, including Anne Klein, Halston, Oscar de la Renta, Stephen Burrows, and Bill Blass, were considered to be more innovative and less traditional than the French designers: Yves Saint Laurent, Hubert de Givenchy, Emanuel Ungaro, Pierre Cardin, and Christian Dior. The American designers ended up winning the competition and solidifying their place in the fashion world. The event was widely covered in the media, and is considered a turning point in the history of fashion. In the game The Battle of Versailles, players take the role of either the France or U.S. team, facing one another by playing action cards to show off their best dresses, to attract the most popular celebrities, or to annoy the opponent by spreading bad gossip. They also compete to contribute more than their opponent to the reconstruction of the palace of Versailles. The French player has five actions per round, representing the classic but overly-long show (2h 30min) that it put on, while the American player has only three actions per round as their show was fresh, innovative, and short (only 37min). Correspondingly, the game has different victory conditions: The French team tries to keep its prestige in the fashion industry, while the American team tries to steal the French prestige. Both teams fight to control the most influential celebrities in the fashion world. The Americans try to show off the best innovative features on their dresses. The French try to contribute as much as possible to the reconstruction of Versailles in order to raise their national pride in this beautiful palace.

title: Salt & Pepper| Conservas | Board Game | Keep Your Canning Business Afloat | Decide Which Fish to Release and Which to Turn into Cans | 1 Player | Spanish | Theme: Meals
description:
About this item
STRATEGIC CANNING AND SUSTAINABILITY GAME - Sail along the coasts of Spain and face challenges to balance your canning business with the conservation of the marine ecosystem. Every decision counts to keep your business afloat and protect the sea!
FUN WITH 12 UNIQUE SCENARIOS - Each game of "Canning" offers you a different challenge with 12 scenarios that feature unique financial and sustainability goals. Each with its own rules and strategies to maintain profitability and the health of the ecosystem.
DYNAMIC PUZZLES IN EACH ROUND - Experience varied gameplay in each round by fishing in a bag of fish and water chips. Decide which fish to release to breed and which to turn into preserves, maintaining a perfect balance.
EDUCATIONAL AND ENTERTAINING BOARD GAME - Ideal for players who enjoy strategy and management. Learn about marine sustainability while having fun, developing decision-making skills and long-term planning.
REPLAYABILITY AND CONSTANT CHALLENGE - Conservas offers a renewable gaming experience with different objectives and strategies in each scenario. Keep you and your friends or family interested with fresh challenges in every playthrough.
› See more product details
desc2: If there is one thing that makes you truly enjoy, then it is to make the treasures that the sea offers accessible to all. You are the owner of a small canning factory sailing along the coasts of Spain, and although it is not very modest to say it, your canned food is recognized throughout the coast. Every month, you face new challenges and try to find the balance between keeping your business and avoiding overfishing. You work hard to get the best preserves in the world! At Conservas you start every fishing season with a boat and some money. The sea is represented by a bag of fish and water marks. In each round, you fish in the bag and decide which fish you leave for breeding and which deserve to be converted into canned food. You must maintain a careful balance to maintain the ecosystem. The game contains 12 scenarios, each of which has unique financial and sustainability goals that you must meet. In addition, each scenario has its own rules and strategies to make it profitable. In Canning, each game offers a different puzzle that you need to solve.

Other Features - The efficient LDPC error correction algorithm (low-density parity check code) effectively enhances the anti-interference ability of data in channel transmission, improves signal transmission efficiency, and makes the connection faster and more stable; Supports WPA-PSK/WPA2-PSK, WPA/WPA2 security mechanism, and WEP encryption to comprehensively protect wireless network security.

description:
About this item
PRECISION - Kailh Midnight Pro silent tactile switches deliver less than 35dB of noise, 45gf of actuation, and 70M keystroke durability; layered foam gaskets minimize pings and echoes
VERSATILE CONTROL & CONNECTIVITY - Seamlessly switch between 2.4GHz wireless, Bluetooth and USB-C; switch between 3 profiles with M keys, adjust settings, RGB and macros; control volume, brightness and media content
LONG LASTING - A 4200mAh battery provides up to 250 hours per charge with the backlight off; the magnetic USB-C adapter offers effortless charging, while USB Gen 3 allows for a full recharge in just 7 hours
DURABLE AND CUSTOMIZABLE - Sublimated PBT keycaps offer durability, fade resistance and a quality feel; Hot-swappable design allows for easy switching of mechanical switches
CUSTOMIZED LIGHTING AND COMFORT - Mystic Light RGB lets you customize colors and effects or sync them to your settings; hotkeys allow you to quickly change lighting and easily access widgets
› See more product details
desc2:
MSI STRIKE PRO WIRELESS - is a top-notch wireless mechanical gaming keyboard designed to enjoy the ultimate gaming experience with extreme accuracy and tactile response to shocks with fast reactions.

Multiple layers of sound dampening foam and precision gaskets are designed to isolate and maintain the authentic sound of each key. This provides a clear and satisfying acoustic experience without annoying noise.

Customizable keyboard layout allows you to swap out default mechanical switches to third-party switches (5 contacts) without soldering.

Sublimated PBT keycaps offer durability, fade resistance and superior typing feel.

Offers 2.4GHz wireless, Bluetooth and wired USB Type-C connection for versatile device compatibility.

The MSI STRIKE PRO WIRELESS offers per-key RGB lighting and is adjustable with MSI Mystic-Light & MSI Center software support (PC only), hotkeys on the fly and a dedicated key for MSI Afterburner (PC only).

Dedicated M keys allow players to easily customize and switch between 3 profiles, including any settings, RGB effects, and macro keys.

Ergonomic high and low key design keeps hands and wrists in a natural position, reducing strain during play. Two keyboard feet support a tilt angle to ensure a more comfortable wrist position during gaming sessions. Enjoy superior comfort with a memory foam wrist rest and magnetic design.

Equipped with a USB-C magnetic adapter, this keyboard offers hassle-free charging.

title: Puig 22145W Mirage Semifairing Clear
description:
Its design with simple and rounded lines combines perfectly with many custom and cruiser motorcycle models, providing an exclusive personalized look and significantly improving the rider's aerodynamic protection.
The Mirage semi-fairing is a very universal accessory since its design easily adapts to motorcycles with a round headlight, covering the front part around the headlight, protecting it from dirt and small impacts.
It allows installing two different screens, the Sport, more aggressive and minimalist, and the Touring screen that provides more aerodynamic protection.
The screens are available in clear, light smoke and dark smoke to match the Mirage semi-fairing which is available in a matte black or gloss black finish.

title: Puig 22107W High-Road Sport Windshield – Aerodynamic Protection and Sporty Design for Harley Davidson Road Glide FLTRX 2024, Clear
description:
About this item
Improve the aerodynamics of your Harley Davidson Road Glide FLTRX 2024 with the Puig 22107W High-Road Sport windshield in clear, designed to reduce turbulence and vibrations, enhancing riding comfort.
Made from high-quality 4mm CN acrylic, it offers excellent impact resistance and maximum transparency, ensuring durability and a perfect integration with the original fairing.
Its wind tunnel-optimized design tilts towards the rider, redirecting airflow and reducing aerodynamic pressure by 30%, improving stability and reducing fatigue on long rides.
Quick and easy installation with no advanced mechanical knowledge required, includes detailed instructions and TÜV certification with ABE approval for street use. Available in multiple finishes.
Compatible Motorcycles: HARLEY DAVIDSON ROAD GLIDE FLTRX 2024.
› See more product details
desc2: The Puig 22107W High-Road Sport windshield in clear is specifically designed to enhance aerodynamic protection and reduce wind turbulence on the Harley Davidson Road Glide FLTRX 2024. Developed using advanced wind tunnel technology, this windshield features a studied inclination that effectively redirects airflow, minimizes turbulence, and reduces aerodynamic pressure on the rider by 30%. The result is a more comfortable riding experience, with fewer helmet vibrations and significantly less fatigue on long journeys. Made from high-quality 4mm CN acrylic, the High-Road Sport windshield stands out for its exceptional impact resistance and excellent transparency, making it an ideal choice for both safety and aesthetics. Its rounded edges provide an elegant finish and comply with the highest homologation standards, including TÜV certification. With dimensions of 145mm in height and 645mm in width, this windshield maintains the same height as the original, ensuring a seamless integration with the stock fairing without altering the bike's original design. Installation is extremely easy and quick, requiring no special tools or advanced mechanical skills, and can be completed in just a few minutes by following the included step-by-step instructions. The High-Road Sport windshield is available in multiple finishes to match every rider's style. It is ABE-approved for legal road use.

desc2:
Escape from the Moon

You were part of a crew working on a moon base, but the other crew members were involved in a mysterious accident during an exploration mission, leaving you alone on the base. The mother ship is in a satellite orbit of the moon. You're completely isolated, alone — when a warning sound rings throughout the base: "There is not much oxygen left. The cause is unknown. Get out of the moon base quickly. To repeat, there's not much oxygen left."

Since the emergency power supply has been activated, it seems that most of the base functions are down due to electrical problems, which means soon the base won't be able to supply you oxygen, let alone communicate an SOS to whoever might be monitoring you.

There is not much time left for activities. Can you restore the rocket in time and return to the mother ship? The challenge to Escape from the Moon begins, with you constructing a deck and managing a hand of possible actions to get yourself to safety, with success or failure depending on the decisions you make and the difficulty of your chosen scenario.

desc2: The new Proto T3 Eclipse throws it back to our roots, featuring the first ever Never Summer logo…The Eclipse. The board itself is anything but a throwback. Full of the latest NS snowboard innovations like our Recurve Triple Camber Profile, setback from center and coupled with an extended nose rocker enhancing our Early-Rise and Float Mechanics. The Precision Stitched Carbon Matrix, aesthetically represented by our T3 Directional Carbon Mapping Embossment, combines advanced materials and cutting-edge design. Blurring the lines between Freeride and Freestyle the Eclipse is purpose built for both ends of the spectrum and everything in-between. You’re immediately at home on the Eclipse because it feels like it was designed precisely for you. Our R.I.P. Edge-Hold Technology, 32 mm setback and 10 mm of taper provide unrivaled stability and lighting response. It’s everything you could want in a board and even more you’re not expecting.

title: Giro TAGGERT MIPS Helm 2025 Matte Black Chrome
description:
About this item
MIPS: el sistema de protección contra impactos multidireccional (Mips) es un paso adelante en el diseño del casco. Hay tres componentes principales para un casco equipado con Mips: el forro interior de espuma, el forro de baja fricción y un sistema de fijación elastomérico entre ellos. En un impacto en ángulo, el sistema de fijación elastomérico se estira para permitir que el forro de espuma gire de forma independiente alrededor de tu cabeza. El objetivo de esta tecnología es reducir aún más las fuerzas de rotación.
I.M. Construcción: I.M. La construcción fusiona una carcasa exterior de policarbonato resistente con el forro de espuma que absorbe los impactos del casco. El proceso de fusión permite mejores sistemas de ventilación, lo que hace que I.M. cascos más ligeros y frescos que los cascos tradicionales.
Sistema de ajuste en forma 2: el sistema de ajuste In Form 2 es más ligero y de perfil más bajo que el original, y más fácil de marcar en un ajuste personalizado en cuestión de segundos, incluso con guantes puestos. Un diseño de esfera mejorado proporciona hasta 6 cm de ajuste y una mayor estabilidad.
Ventilación agresiva pasiva: el diseño discreto de ventilación exterior y la canalización interior (incluyendo el forro y el acolchado) se combinan para crear un flujo de aire óptimo y regulación de temperatura. Esta tecnología de ventilación automática gestiona el flujo de aire y el movimiento de la temperatura, el senderismo, o la estática de pie.
Características: Mips. Compatible con sistemas de audio de posventa. Almohadillas extraíbles. Retenedor de gafas extraíble. Sintonización vertical.

title: Giro Jackson MIPS Ski/Snow Helmet, Men
description:
About this item
MIPS - Multi-directional impact protection system can provide more protection in certain impacts. The main components of a MIPS equipped helmet are 1. The inner foam lining, 2. The low-friction lining, and 3. an elastomeric fastening system. In an angled impact, the elastomeric attachment system stretches to allow the foam liner to rotate independently around your head.
In-mold construction fuses a tough polycarbonate outer shell with the helmet's impact-absorbing foam lining. The fusion process allows for better ventilation systems, making In-Mold helmets lighter and cooler than traditional helmets.
Form Fit System 2 - Lighter and lower profile than the original, and easier to dial in a custom fit in seconds, even with gloves on. An improved dial design provides up to 6cm of adjustment and enhanced stability.
Passive Aggressive Ventilation System - The discreet exterior ventilation design and interior channeling combine to create optimal airflow and temperature regulation. This automatic ventilation technology manages airflow and temperature while driving, hiking or standing static.
With 215g gravity defying with the performance and adjustment range you need to conquer the steepest routes ahead, the Imperial is destined to lead a lightweight revolution in road cycling footwear.

title: Giro Jackson MIPS Ski/Snow Helmet, Men
description:
About this item
MIPS - Multi-directional impact protection system can provide more protection in certain impacts. The main components of a MIPS equipped helmet are 1. The inner foam lining, 2. The low-friction lining, and 3. an elastomeric fastening system. In an angled impact, the elastomeric attachment system stretches to allow the foam liner to rotate independently around your head.
In-mold construction fuses a tough polycarbonate outer shell with the helmet's impact-absorbing foam lining. The fusion process allows for better ventilation systems, making In-Mold helmets lighter and cooler than traditional helmets.
Form Fit System 2 - Lighter and lower profile than the original, and easier to dial in a custom fit in seconds, even with gloves on. An improved dial design provides up to 6cm of adjustment and enhanced stability.
Passive Aggressive Ventilation System - The discreet exterior ventilation design and interior channeling combine to create optimal airflow and temperature regulation. This automatic ventilation technology manages airflow and temperature while driving, hiking or standing static.
With 215g gravity defying with the performance and adjustment range you need to conquer the steepest routes ahead, the Imperial is destined to lead a lightweight revolution in road cycling footwear.

title: Giro Tor Snow Helmet, Unisex Adult
description:
About this item
Spherical Technology - MIPS-powered spherical technology ball and cube design helps redirect impact forces away from the brain by allowing the outer liner to rotate around the inner liner during a crash. It also eliminates contact with hard plastic or planes sliding against the skin.
HYBRID CONSTRUCTION - Hybrid construction combines a durable, ventilated upper with an I.M. Bottom shell construction plus sidewalls for added protection and style. With hybrid construction, the helmet is reinforced for durability while remaining lightweight. The hybrid construction also features a lightweight, impact-absorbing EPS foam liner.

title: Giro TAGGERT MIPS Helm 2025 Matte Black Chrome
description:
About this item
MIPS: el sistema de protección contra impactos multidireccional (Mips) es un paso adelante en el diseño del casco. Hay tres componentes principales para un casco equipado con Mips: el forro interior de espuma, el forro de baja fricción y un sistema de fijación elastomérico entre ellos. En un impacto en ángulo, el sistema de fijación elastomérico se estira para permitir que el forro de espuma gire de forma independiente alrededor de tu cabeza. El objetivo de esta tecnología es reducir aún más las fuerzas de rotación.
I.M. Construcción: I.M. La construcción fusiona una carcasa exterior de policarbonato resistente con el forro de espuma que absorbe los impactos del casco. El proceso de fusión permite mejores sistemas de ventilación, lo que hace que I.M. cascos más ligeros y frescos que los cascos tradicionales.
Sistema de ajuste en forma 2: el sistema de ajuste In Form 2 es más ligero y de perfil más bajo que el original, y más fácil de marcar en un ajuste personalizado en cuestión de segundos, incluso con guantes puestos. Un diseño de esfera mejorado proporciona hasta 6 cm de ajuste y una mayor estabilidad.
Ventilación agresiva pasiva: el diseño discreto de ventilación exterior y la canalización interior (incluyendo el forro y el acolchado) se combinan para crear un flujo de aire óptimo y regulación de temperatura. Esta tecnología de ventilación automática gestiona el flujo de aire y el movimiento de la temperatura, el senderismo, o la estática de pie.
Características: Mips. Compatible con sistemas de audio de posventa. Almohadillas extraíbles. Retenedor de gafas extraíble. Sintonización vertical.

About this item

Armed with our In Form 2 fit system, the Owen allows riders to quickly adjust the helmet size, while also adjusting the vertical fit. title: Giro Buster Ski Mask Kids
description:
About this item
EXPANSION VIEW (EXV) TECHNOLOGY — Perfected at Giro's test lab in Scotts Valley, California, this groundbreaking new frame design serves up unparalleled peripheral vision. We started with a helmet-compatible goggle, and then shaved down the frame rim and added frameless zones to optimize a massive spherical lens focused on the best possible peripheral vision in a goggle.
INJECTION-MOLDED CYLINDRICAL LENSES — Injection-molding a cylindrical lens helps refine optics and minimize distortion that can occur in thermo-formed cylindrical lenses.
OTG FRIENDLY — Engineered specifically for bespectacled skiers and snowboarders, goggles that are OTG (Over-The-Glasses) feature a finely crafted interior with extra volume to accommodate prescription frames comfortably. Increased air volume inside the goggle keeps your vision crisp, clear, and fog-free.
TRIPLE-LAYER FACE FOAM — Triple Layer face foam with microfleece facing
SEAMLESS COMPATIBILITY — For optimal performance of both helmets and goggles, Giro products are designed to work together, ensuring a seamless interface between helmet and goggle for an exceptional fit and dependable, worry-free function.

title: Giro Unisex Chico 2.0 Goggles (pack of 1)
description:
About this item
YOUTH SIZE EXTRA-SMALL FRAME - Toddler size Kids Ski and Snowboard Goggles for boys and girls age 2-4 years old.
DOUBLE-LAYER FACE FOAM -Double Layer face foam with microfleece facing to give your grom all day comfort on the slopes.
SEAMLESS COMPATIBILITY WITH GIRO TODDLER SKI HELMETS - For optimal performance of both helmets and goggles, Giro products are designed to work together, ensuring a seamless interface between helmet and goggle for an exceptional fit and dependable, worry-free function. Pair these up with the Giro Crue Mips, Spur Mips, or Neo Jr Mips Kids Helmet for the ultimate set up for your shredder.
PRESSFIT LENS INTERCHANGE SYSMEM - Allows you to easily replace scratched lenses or change into a different color lens for your kids' maximum enjoyment on the mountain.
ADDITIONAL FEATURES - Kid Approved Styling, Silicone on the inside of the strap to prevent slippage and ensure that it stays in place over your helmet.
desc2: The Giro Chico is designed for the smallest shredders so they can fully enjoy their first turns. The double lens is equipped with an anti-fog coating and the cosy face pad made of foam and microfleece offers reliable protection from the cold. In addition, the Chico can be seamlessly combined with the Crüe MIPS and Launch MIPS kids' helmet.

title: Fischer Scarponi da sci RC90 – Flex 90 – Scarponi da sci alpinismo – Stivali da sci alpinismo – vestibilità ampia – per piloti avanzati e buoni
description:
Il modello RC90 nero è lo scarpone da sci perfetto per gli sciatori con piedi larghi che cercano sia prestazioni che comfort. Sia che tu stia viaggiando su piste preparate o esplorando vari terreni montuosi, questa scarpa è fatta su misura per le tue esigenze.
RC90 è uno scarpone da sci ad alte prestazioni con una linea larga che offre spazio sufficiente anche ai piedi più larghi senza compromettere il controllo. Grazie al suo design sportivo e morbido, offre un elevato comfort e rende le lunghe giornate sulle piste ancora più piacevoli.
La struttura leggera e il facile accesso consentono di salire e scendere senza sforzo, in modo da poterti concentrare completamente sul divertimento degli sci. L'aletta Floating Entry consente un accesso e un'uscita particolarmente leggeri, mentre il collo del piede più alto e la punta offrono maggiore spazio e comfort, riducendo i punti di pressione e ottimizzando la vestibilità.
Provate il perfetto mix di prestazioni e comfort con il RC 90 – questo scarpone da sci progettato per aiutarvi a godervi ogni momento in montagna. Offre la presa e la facilità d'uso di cui hanno bisogno gli sciatori amatoriali con i piedi larghi.

title: Cecotec Bolero Squad G 2400F Stainless Steel Gas Hob, 5.2 kW, Cast Iron Grills with Stainless Steel, WOK Triple Burner, Electronic Ignition, Safety Valves, Conversion Accessory
description:
About this item
The Cecotec Bolero Squad G 2400F Stainless Steel Gas Hob is the perfect addition to any kitchen looking to combine elegance and functionality. With a power of 5.2kW, it offers fast and precise cooking, ideal for those who want perfect results in less time.
This model features two burners, perfect for smaller kitchens or for those who prefer to concentrate on a single saucer at a time. Its sleek stainless steel finish will not only enhance the look of your kitchen, but it is also incredibly durable and easy to clean.
Full cast iron grills offer maximum stability and strength, ensuring a solid base for your pots and pans, withstanding daily use without wear and tear. In addition, the WOK triple crown burner ensures even heat distribution, perfect for dishes that require intense cooking.

title: Puig 22333R R-Racer windscreen with professional aerodynamic design, high-impact acrylic material, rounded profile, easy installation and TÜV approval for road use, Red
description:
About this item
Puig 22333R R-Racer windscreen in red color made of 3 mm high-impact acrylic with rounded edge over 2 mm. Designed for sport bikes, offering top performance and racing aesthetics.
Measures 385 mm high by 280 mm wide, with a height 50 mm greater than the original. Improves aerodynamics by deflecting wind from the helmet and shoulders, increasing high-speed stability.
Tested in a virtual wind tunnel to ensure improvement in the Cx aerodynamic coefficient. Used by professional MotoGP and WorldSBK teams, guarantees clear vision and superior track performance.
Manufactured in Barcelona with advanced technology, artificial vision for quality control, and no need for edge trim. Includes ABE license, mounting instructions, and detailed aerodynamic study.
Compatible motorcycles: DUCATI PANIGALE V4 2025; DUCATI PANIGALE V4S 2025
› See more product details
desc2: The Puig R-Racer windscreen, reference 22333R in red, is the result of years of experience in high-level competition, developed in collaboration with teams like Repsol Honda Team in MotoGP and Kawasaki Racing Team in WorldSBK. Specifically designed for sport motorcycles, this windscreen enhances aerodynamic performance and provides clear visibility thanks to its optimized shape. Manufactured in Barcelona using the most advanced technologies and made from 3 mm high-impact acrylic, it offers the perfect combination of strength, lightness, and durability. Its rounded upper edge of over 2 mm complies with the German TÜV safety standards. With dimensions of 385 x 280 mm, it is 50 mm taller than the original screen, helping to deflect wind that would normally hit the rider's helmet and shoulders. This translates into greater stability at high speeds and less fatigue during sporty riding. Each unit undergoes a rigorous quality control process using artificial vision to ensure it reaches the customer in perfect condition. It does not require trim or additional parts for installation, making the process easy. It also includes a detailed aerodynamic study showing actual improvements over the original screen. With ABE certification, this windscreen is fully street legal. It is the ideal choice for riders seeking professional-level performance without sacrificing style or safety.

title: SIGMA Aura 50 | Luz LED para Bicicleta con 50 Lux y USB-C | Luz Delantera con 2 Modos de iluminación y Ajuste automático de la luz | Batería de Larga duración
description:
About this item
LÁMPARA DE LARGA DURACIÓN: la AURA 50 dispone de dos modos de iluminación. En el modo alto, ilumina de forma fiable hasta 9 horas, y en el modo ECO, ¡hasta 28 horas! Gracias a la función de memoria, la AURA 50 se enciende la próxima vez tal y como se apagó la última vez.
CLEVER: la luz delantera piensa por sí misma. En el modo automático, un sensor de luminosidad integrado regula automáticamente la intensidad de la luz en función de la luz ambiental. De este modo, se garantiza siempre una iluminación óptima y se aprovecha la batería de forma especialmente eficiente.
RECARGABLE: la Aura 50 cuenta con una batería recargable integrada. La luz delantera se puede recargar completamente en 3 horas a través de USB-C. Esto ahorra dinero y protege el medio ambiente. Basta con pulsar brevemente el botón y el indicador LED de tres niveles muestra el estado actual de la batería. Gracias a la pantalla, los ciclistas también pueden controlar el progreso durante la carga.
PROTECCIÓN CONTRA EL ENCENDIDO ACCIDENTAL: la linterna se enciende con un doble clic y se apaga manteniendo pulsado el botón. Esta función evita que se active accidentalmente, por ejemplo, en la mochila escolar o en la mochila.
FÁCIL MONTAJE: gracias al soporte de silicona ajustable en 360°, la AURA 50 se fija al manillar en cuestión de segundos y sin necesidad de herramientas. Se puede orientar horizontal y verticalmente según sea necesario. Para que la luz se pueda guardar aún más rápido y ahorrando espacio, está equipada con un sistema de «liberación rápida», lo que permite retirarla mientras el soporte permanece fijado a la bicicleta.
RESISTENTE A LA INTEMPERIE: la AURA 50 es ideal para cualquier aventura en bicicleta. Cuenta con protección contra salpicaduras según IP44, lo que la hace perfecta para cualquier condición meteorológica en el tráfico urbano.
VISIBILIDAD: la guía de luz lateral no solo es un elemento destacado desde el punto de vista óptico. Los dos LED adicionales garantizan una visibilidad lateral mucho mayor.
SOSTENIBLE: la luz delantera cumple los requisitos del Reglamento sobre pilas y acumuladores de la UE. La carcasa atornillada permite que el cambio de la batería sea realizado por personal autorizado, lo que garantiza una mayor sostenibilidad y seguridad.

title: MT Helmets Lite – Casco Moto Infantil Ligero y Seguro con Interior Lavable, Cierre Micrométrico y Calota HIRP | Ideal para Scooter o Quad | Homologado ECE 22.06
description:
🛡️ Máxima protección con homologación ECE 22.06 INFANTIL y DOT Casco de moto infantil certificado bajo la nueva normativa ECE 22.06 y DOT. Su calota está fabricada en HIRP (High Impact Resistant Polymer), material ligero de alta resistencia frente a impactos. El cierre micrométrico MT-MDTC de doble anclaje evita aperturas accidentales y ofrece máxima seguridad con un uso cómodo y práctico.
🕶️ Pantalla envolvente para máxima visibilidad y protección 🧒✨ Pantalla clara de policarbonato óptico antirayaduras con diseño envolvente, ideal para proteger del viento, el polvo y pequeñas partículas. Proporciona un campo visual amplio y seguro para los más pequeños. Sistema de anclaje resistente, fácil de accionar por un adulto para mayor practicidad.
💨 Ventilación funcional y ajuste infantil ergonómico 🧒🌬️ Diseñado para niños, el MT Lite cuenta con entrada de aire superior que mantiene el interior fresco y ventilado durante trayectos cortos o prolongados. Su calota y acolchados están adaptados a tallas infantiles, ofreciendo un ajuste ergonómico, cómodo y estable que mejora tanto la protección como el confort en movimiento.
🧒 Casco infantil ligero y divertido para pequeños riders 🎨🏍️ Diseñado exclusivamente para niños, el MT Lite ofrece una estructura ligera, segura y con tallas adaptadas a los más pequeños. Su diseño colorido y su confort lo convierten en la opción ideal para que los más jóvenes viajen protegidos y con estilo desde sus primeras aventuras en moto.
🧼 Interior ergonómico, antibacteriano y lavable 🧵🧒 Diseñado para niños, su interior desmontable y lavable está confeccionado con tejidos hipoalergénicos y antibacterianos, pensados para el uso diario. El acolchado se adapta a tallas infantiles, proporcionando un ajuste seguro, cómodo y estable durante la conducción, ideal para mantener la higiene y el confort en cada salida.
desc2: 🧒 MT Lite – Casco Infantil Ligero, Seguro y Divertido El MT Lite es un casco jet diseñado específicamente para niños, pensado para ofrecer la máxima seguridad y comodidad desde los primeros trayectos en moto. Con un diseño compacto y peso reducido, está adaptado a las necesidades de los más pequeños, tanto en talla como en ergonomía. Su estructura cumple con los más altos estándares de protección bajo la homologación ECE 22.06, brindando confianza a padres y tutores. 🔧 Especificaciones técnicas: -Tipo de casco: Jet / Infantil -Material de la calota: HIRP – High Impact Resistant Polymer -Calota: Compacta, específica para niños -Peso aproximado: Muy ligero, ideal para cuellos en desarrollo -Homologación: ECE 22.06 🛡️ Seguridad y estructura: -Calota HIRP para alta resistencia al impacto con peso optimizado -EPS de densidad variable para mejor absorción de energía -Cierre micrométrico de fácil uso, ideal para manos pequeñas -Visor claro para protección visual frontal 🌬️ Ventilación y confort: -Entradas de aire superiores y canalización interna -Ventilación diseñada para mantener el confort térmico sin sobrecargar al usuario 🧼 Interior y ergonomía: -Interior desmontable y lavable -Tejidos hipoalergénicos y antibacterianos -Acolchados adaptados a tallas infantiles para mejor ajuste y estabilidad -Diseño anatómico específico para cabezas de niños 🎨 Estilo y diseño: -Gráficos coloridos y acabados brillantes o mate según versión -Ideal para personalizar y generar entusiasmo en los más pequeños 📦 Contenido del producto: -1 casco MT Lite -Funda protectora -Manual de usuario -Adhesivos decorativos MT Helmets El MT Lite es la opción perfecta para introducir a los niños al mundo de las dos ruedas con seguridad, confort y estilo. Un casco pensado para proteger a los pequeños riders sin renunciar a la diversión.

💨 Ventilación funcional y ajuste infantil ergonómico 🧒🌬️ Diseñado para niños, el MT Lite cuenta con entrada de aire superior que mantiene el interior fresco y ventilado durante trayectos cortos o prolongados. Su calota y acolchados están adaptados a tallas infantiles, ofreciendo un ajuste ergonómico, cómodo y estable que mejora tanto la protección como el confort en movimiento.
🧒 Casco infantil ligero y divertido para pequeños riders 🎨🏍️ Diseñado exclusivamente para niños, el MT Lite ofrece una estructura ligera, segura y con tallas adaptadas a los más pequeños. Su diseño colorido y su confort lo convierten en la opción ideal para que los más jóvenes viajen protegidos y con estilo desde sus primeras aventuras en moto.
🧼 Interior ergonómico, antibacteriano y lavable 🧵🧒 Diseñado para niños, su interior desmontable y lavable está confeccionado con tejidos hipoalergénicos y antibacterianos, pensados para el uso diario. El acolchado se adapta a tallas infantiles, proporcionando un ajuste seguro, cómodo y estable durante la conducción, ideal para mantener la higiene y el confort en cada salida.
desc2: 🧒 MT Lite – Casco Infantil Ligero, Seguro y Divertido El MT Lite es un casco jet diseñado específicamente para niños, pensado para ofrecer la máxima seguridad y comodidad desde los primeros trayectos en moto. Con un diseño compacto y peso reducido, está adaptado a las necesidades de los más pequeños, tanto en talla como en ergonomía. Su estructura cumple con los más altos estándares de protección bajo la homologación ECE 22.06, brindando confianza a padres y tutores. 🔧 Especificaciones técnicas: -Tipo de casco: Jet / Infantil -Material de la calota: HIRP – High Impact Resistant Polymer -Calota: Compacta, específica para niños -Peso aproximado: Muy ligero, ideal para cuellos en desarrollo -Homologación: ECE 22.06 🛡️ Seguridad y estructura: -Calota HIRP para alta resistencia al impacto con peso optimizado -EPS de densidad variable para mejor absorción de energía -Cierre micrométrico de fácil uso, ideal para manos pequeñas -Visor claro para protección visual frontal 🌬️ Ventilación y confort: -Entradas de aire superiores y canalización interna -Ventilación diseñada para mantener el confort térmico sin sobrecargar al usuario 🧼 Interior y ergonomía: -Interior desmontable y lavable -Tejidos hipoalergénicos y antibacterianos -Acolchados adaptados a tallas infantiles para mejor ajuste y estabilidad -Diseño anatómico específico para cabezas de niños 🎨 Estilo y diseño: -Gráficos coloridos y acabados brillantes o mate según versión -Ideal para personalizar y generar entusiasmo en los más pequeños 📦 Contenido del producto: -1 casco MT Lite -Funda protectora -Manual de usuario -Adhesivos decorativos MT Helmets El MT Lite es la opción perfecta para introducir a los niños al mundo de las dos ruedas con seguridad, confort y estilo. Un casco pensado para proteger a los pequeños riders sin renunciar a la diversión.

title: Giro Ratio Ski Helmet - Snowboard Helmet for Men, Women & Youth - Matte Black - M (55.5–59cm)
description:
About this item
HARD SHELL CONSTRUCTION — Hard Shell Construction produces great helmets at a great price. A rugged outer shell is molded and then attached to the EPS foam liner.
SEAMLESS COMPATIBILITY — For optimal performance of both helmets and goggles, Giro products are designed to work together, ensuring a seamless interface between helmet and goggle for an exceptional fit and dependable, worry-free function.
STACK VENT TECHNOLOGY — Our Stack Vent was developed based on research showing the majority of warm air that can cause fogging comes from the goggle's center top vent. Aligning the Stack Vent in the helmet with the center vent of the goggle helps keep it clear and fog-free.
THERMOSTAT CONTROL — Thermostat Control Adjustable Venting allows you to custom-tune airflow instantly with a simple, low profile control button on the outside of the helmet. No other system is faster or easier to adjust, and nothing is more effective at keeping you comfortable.
IN FORM FIT SYSTEM — The In Form Fit System makes it easy to dial in a custom fit in seconds - even with gloves on. An ergo-friendly dial at the base of the helmet provides up to 6cm of adjustment and enhanced stability.
desc2: Beneath the sleek silhouette, you'll find the adjustability of an In Form fit system and Thermostat Control adjustable venting. Meanwhile, the Ratio helmet is also fully compatibility with aftermarket audio systems by Outdoor Tech so you can listen to your favorite tunes on the mountain.

WOMEN'S ALL-MOUNTAIN SKIS - Designed for women moving from beginner to intermediate, the Volkl Shine 76 offers a 76mm waist for easy handling on groomed runs, balanced with stability and control that supports progression into more dynamic skiing as skills and confidence improve
RESPONSIVE WOODCORE CONSTRUCTION - Built with a lightweight woodcore inlay reinforced by PU, this ski ensures consistent flex, smooth turn initiation, and dependable edge hold, adapting to developing technique for a ride that remains stable, forgiving, and responsive on all terrain
PARTIAL SIDEWALL & 3D RIDGE DESIGN - Engineered with a center sidewall for powerful transmission and enhanced control, combined with a slim 3D.Ridge design that minimizes weight while maintaining grip and precision, delivering agility and maneuverability for evolving skiers
PREMIUM BASE & STRUCTURE - Features a sintered P-Tex 2100 base with excellent glide, durability, and long-term performance, plus Zebra Structure tuning for precise carving, controlled drifting, and smooth transitions, making every piste run reliable, fast, and performance driven
VMOTION1 BINDINGS INCLUDED - Equipped with factory-mounted vMotion1 bindings compatible with GripWalk soles, offering secure boot connection, efficient power transfer, and immediate out-of-box readiness, so skiers can enjoy stability, safety, and enhanced skiing confidence
desc2:
Elevate your skiing progression with the Volkl Shine 76 Women's Skis, part of the 2026 collection. Designed for beginner and intermediate skiers, these skis feature a versatile 76mm waist that provides the perfect balance between stability and agility. The Tip Rocker profile ensures easy turn initiation, while the camber underfoot enhances grip and energy for smooth carving.

Engineered for performance and durability, the Shine 76 incorporates a woodcore inlay reinforced with PU, combining lightweight responsiveness with consistent flex. The Center Sidewall construction delivers strong power transmission where it matters most, while the 3D.Ridge design minimizes unnecessary weight for effortless maneuverability.

Performance-driven details include: a sintered P-Tex 2100 base for outstanding glide and wear resistance, plus Zebra Structure for optimized edge control, reliable carving precision, and smooth transitions. Each ski arrives with a factory Serial Finish, ensuring it is tuned and ready to perform from day one.

Complete with vMotion1 bindings, this ski package supports GripWalk compatibility and efficient power transfer, giving skiers a secure and confidence-inspiring ride. The Volkl Shine 76 makes exploring the mountain more accessible and rewarding, encouraging new adventures as skills grow.

description:
About this item
Pulverizador agua de 1,5L – Capacidad compacta para uso doméstico, perfecta como pulverizador jardín o pulverizador de agua para plantas de interior, balcón o terraza.

Gatillo ergonómico – Diseño cómodo para usar como borrifador de agua o fumigadora pulverizador ligera, reduciendo la fatiga en sesiones largas.
Recipiente translúcido con medidas – Depósito visible que facilita controlar el nivel de líquidos, ideal como botella pulverizador para fertilizantes o productos de limpieza.

desc2: El pulverizador TATAY 1,5L es la herramienta ideal para quienes buscan practicidad y eficiencia en el cuidado de plantas y en el hogar. Su diseño ligero y compacto lo convierte en un pulverizador jardín perfecto para uso diario, tanto en interiores como en exteriores. Gracias a su versatilidad, puede emplearse como sulfatadora manual para aplicar tratamientos fitosanitarios, como fumigadora pulverizador para mantener hojas sanas, o como borrifador para mantener la humedad en ambientes secos. Además, su depósito translúcido lo hace ideal como botella pulverizador, permitiendo controlar el nivel de agua o fertilizante en todo momento. Este pulverizador manual combina comodidad y seguridad: la boquilla ajustable se adapta a diferentes necesidades, mientras que la válvula de seguridad integrada garantiza un uso fiable. También es un excelente borrifador de agua para la limpieza ligera de ventanas, baños o superficies delicadas. Con la garantía de calidad TATAY, este pulverizador de agua ofrece una solución duradera y ergonómica para tus tareas de jardinería, cuidado de plantas y limpieza doméstica.
